Class Vec2.ComparatorDist

java.lang.Object
camzup.core.Vec2.AbstrComparator
camzup.core.Vec2.ComparatorDist
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.util.Comparator<Vec2>
Enclosing class:
Vec2
public static class Vec2.ComparatorDist
extends Vec2.AbstrComparator
Compares two vectors by their distance from a locus. The locus should be set in the creation of the comparator.
